It is the single source of truth ‚Äî IDE-specific config files should reference this.

## Project Context

- **Project**: {% for word in plugin_name | split(pat='-') %}{{ word | capitalize }}{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %} ‚Äî {{ plugin_description }}
- **Architecture**: React 18 (TypeScript) frontend{% if has_wasm %} + Rust WASM{% endif %} Grafana {{ plugin_type }} plugin{% if has_docker %} ‚Äî Docker dev environment included{% endif %}{% if has_mock %} ‚Äî mock data tooling included{% endif %}
